VCam Media Directory
====================
Place your test media files here:
  - Images: .jpg, .jpeg, .png, .heic
  - Videos: .mp4, .mov, .m4v

Configure in: Settings > VCam > Media Filename

Example:
  1. Copy test_face.mp4 to this directory
  2. Settings > VCam > Media Type = Video
  3. Settings > VCam > Media Filename = test_face.mp4
  4. Open target app camera — done!
